    <h2 class="sect-title">About Tuscany</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Established back in the year 1994, Tuscany homes can boast of being in one of the few best selling communities in the North West neighborhood of Calgary real estate. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">Tuscany has acquired the 11th ranking among Calgaryâ€™s best neighborhoods according to Avenue Magazine.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Complete with stunning mountain views, a world-class private community center and a natural ravine system sprawled across 170 acres, the community in Tuscany can be rightly touted as one of the most sought neighborhoods of the NW.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Keeping in mind the comfort and convenience of both the young and the elderly, Tuscany homes for sale include everything from $300,000 townhouses, apartments, single family homes, senior housing to the more upscale luxury Estate and Executive bungalows of around $1 million.</p>
